metadata.name: Cirlia
metadata.description: Cirlia is an elf who lived in the City of Yuura. Yuura is a city of peace and riches, but devastation occurred when the city was turned into ashes. Cirlia lost everything and everyone she knows. Finding refuge in the City of Chroma, She trained and joined the military. When her memories of losing her mother and home appear in her mind, she always remembers her favorite flower tree. It was a place she felt most at peace.
